{"success":true,"result":{"Q_10110765467085-1":{"resources":[],"questions":[{"id":"Q_10110765467085-1","subjectId":101,"knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[{"id":"KP_10100096572431","tagId":0,"main":1,"featureIds":[]},{"id":"KP_10100096773750","tagId":0,"main":1,"featureIds":[]},{"id":"KP_10100096779452","tagId":0,"main":1,"featureIds":[]},{"id":"KP_10100096786918","tagId":0,"main":1,"featureIds":[]}],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000673226","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"resourceIds":null,"resourceIndex":0,"listenUrl":null,"listenName":null,"listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"paperIds":["P_10100141696037-1","P_10100141696037-2","P_10100141696037-3"],"books":null,"booksNew":null,"contentTypeId":1010008,"contentType2Id":0,"difficultyInt":3,"description":"阅读课外文章，回答问题","notFitMobile":0,"seconds":540,"complex":1,"nid":null,"lastEditorId":null,"finalAuditorId":null,"roughAuditorIds":null,"content":{"content":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>是谁把强盗引入了圆明园</strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">近日读史，看到清代伟大爱国诗人龚自珍之子龚半伦的一段丑事，颇有感触。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">龚自珍作为爱国诗人而名垂青史，可是他万万没有想到，在他去世后，逆子龚半伦却卖国求荣，成了侵略者的帮凶。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">据《清朝野史大观》、《圆明园残毁考》等载：1860年，英法联军侵入中国，龚半伦随英舰北上来到北京后，将辫发盘到头顶，戴洋人帽，穿白色西装，出入洋兵营盘，狐假虎威，好不得意。随后，他将联军引进圆明园，并抢先一步单骑直入，取珍宝重器以归，大发横财。然后，就有了那场震惊中外的大火…… 这场大火燃烧了一百多年，直到今天还烧得所有的中国人心痛，也让世界上所有有良知的人心痛。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">与龚半伦形成鲜明对比的是他的父亲龚自珍。父子俩一个爱国，一个卖国，一个名垂青史，一个遗臭万年。清人赵翼说， 名父之子多败德，这虽然不是必然规律，但名父不幸而有逆子，按照“子不教父之过”的说法，龚自珍自然也难辞其咎。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">一家如此，一国也如此。古往今来，无数仁人志士以爱国为荣，谱写了一曲曲爱国主义的壮歌；也有汉奸、走狗、卖国贼引狼入室，认贼作父。戚继光，抗击倭寇，出生入死，“一年三百六十日，都是横戈马上行”；林则徐，临危受命，“苟利国家生死以，岂因祸福避趋之”；左宗棠以花甲之年，请缨出征，抬着棺材行军，率部收复新疆大片领土；杨靖宇，战斗在白山黑水，英勇无畏，洒尽最后一滴血；狼牙山五壮士，宁死不屈，惊天地，泣鬼神……国难当头，也难免有像秦桧、龚半伦、汪精卫那样的大小汉奸沉渣泛起，为虎作伥；和平年代，照样有种种危害祖国的行为存在，我们仍不能掉以轻心。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">“尔曹身与名俱灭，不废江河万古流。”历史代谢，人事更迭，但无论怎样沧海桑田，爱国志士都将永远被人纪念景仰，爱国精神将永远成为中华民族宝贵的精神财富。而那些危害祖国的历史罪人，不论以什么形式出现，都是极其可耻而不可饶恕的，他们最终必然身败名裂，受到人民的惩罚。</p>","contentDesc":"","analysis":"","subContents":[{"content":"<p>依序写出第4自然段中的一对四字反义词。</p><p>__$$__——__$$__</p>","answers":[{"answer":"名垂青史","subAnswers":["名垂青史"],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000632696","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null},{"answer":"遗臭万年","subAnswers":["遗臭万年"],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000632696","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":4,"analysis":"","optionType":"word","options":[],"hideOptionNumber":0,"listenUrl":"","listenName":"","listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"oralDict":{"seconds":null,"variables":null,"keywords":null,"options":null,"voiceText":null,"sentencePatterns":null,"picUrl":null,"picName":null,"beginListenUrl":null,"endListenUrl":null,"scorePercentage":null,"readySeconds":null,"listenFile":null,"contentDesc":null,"answers":null,"voiceTextsNew":null,"jsgf":null,"videoUrl":null,"videoCoverUrl":null,"highlightPos":null},"submitWays":[0],"tags":[101007],"analysisList":null,"pictureUrl":"","extras":{},"tagsDesc":["其他"]},{"content":"这篇短文主要讲述了一件什么历史事实？","answers":[{"answer":"1","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":1,"analysis":"","optionType":"sentence","options":[{"option":"英法联军侵入中国，并火烧圆明园。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"爱国诗人龚自珍的儿子龚半伦将英法联军引进了圆明园。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}}],"hideOptionNumber":0,"listenUrl":"","listenName":"","listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"oralDict":{"seconds":null,"variables":null,"keywords":null,"options":null,"voiceText":null,"sentencePatterns":null,"picUrl":null,"